                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, etc. Ut in
                            <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
